      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BIG BOY PANTS (4) hit the ground running to win over the 390m at Warrnambool two runs back then raced on speed again when finishing third at this track last start. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from four attempts. Likely to feature again. BREAKN' A SWEAT (6) is having his first start around this circuit. In the money last start when third (24.82) at Sale over 435m. Will give a great sight again. VOLTS (2) finished second (23.16) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 8th there. Has a good record here at this journey. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to his credit. Likely to play a prominent role.",
